 Judas Priest 的 Rob Halford 不打算很快退休：“我不知道该怎么办我的生活” https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priests-rob-halford-isnt-planning-on-retiring-anytime-soon-3792181?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=judas-priests-rob-halford-不打算很快退休Surej SinghTue, 10 Sep 2024 07:22:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3792181 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗伯·哈尔福德 (Rob Halford)，犹大圣徒乐队主唱" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “只要它看起来不错，听起来不错，而且其他所有部件都已到位，你为什么要退休呢？”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priests-rob-halford-isnt-planning-on-retiring-anytime-soon-3792181">《犹大圣徒》的罗布·哈尔福德不打算很快退休：“我不知道我的人生该怎么办”，这</a>句话首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗伯·哈尔福德 (Rob Halford)，犹大圣徒乐队主唱" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/rob-halford-judas-priest@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">犹大圣徒 (Judas Priest</a> ) 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rob-halford">罗布·哈尔福德 (Rob Halford)</a>不会很快挂靴——看看这位传奇金属歌手对退休有何看法。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/judas-priest-rob-halford-heavy-metal-3594311">犹大牧师传奇人物罗布·哈尔福德：“出柜是以正确的方式发生的 - 这不是有预谋的”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位犹大牧师主唱最近接受了爱荷华州的<em>Rock 108</em>采访，谈到了他是否打算很快退休。正如<a href="https://www.loudersound.com/news/rob-halford-has-no-plans-to-retire-while-judas-priest-can-still-deliver-the-goods" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《经典摇滚》</em></a>所记录的，哈尔福德说：“我认为，如果你的愿望依然存在，如果你的激情依然存在，如果你仍然能够交付货物——引用一首牧师的歌曲——如果你在前进而机器却没有太摇晃了，你仍然可以用一个轮子从A到B，只要它看起来不错，听起来不错，并且所有其他部件都就位，你为什么要退休呢？ </p><figure id="attachment_3789976" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3789976" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3789976" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/judas-priest@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Judas Priest 的 Rob Halford 将于 2024 年现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/judas-priest@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/judas-priest@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/judas-priest@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/judas-priest@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/judas-priest@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/judas-priest@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3789976" class="wp-caption-text">犹大圣徒的罗布·哈尔福德。图片来源：Per Ole Hagen/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道：“如果我突然不能完成这项美丽的工作，我将不知道我的生活该怎么办。我需要这样做。这是我作为一个人生活所需要做的一部分，因为我非常喜欢它。我想我是在代表 Priest 的每个人说话。这就是穿透的主光。这就是让你坚持下去的动力。”</p><p>哈尔福德接着说，犹大牧师不愿退休的部分原因是他们仍然从热爱的粉丝群体中汲取能量：“你立即将其与我们在美国和世界各地的光荣粉丝结合在一起，正是这些粉丝让这台重金属机器不断运转，因为我们无法单独做到这一点。如果里面没有人，我们进入竞技场就会显得很愚蠢。你需要那里的人。这是体验的一部分。它让你变得完整。一场现场表演让你对乐队的热爱更加完整。”</p><p>最近，乐队贝斯手 Ian Hill 表示 Judas Priest <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priest-are-re-mixing-and-re-releasing-their-debut-album-rocka-rolla-3789975">正在重新混音他们的首张专辑《Rocka Rolla》，该专辑刚刚成立 50 周年</a>：“我相信这张专辑很快就会发行。距离发布只有几周了，我确定……它将被重新发布，这是个好消息。它终于得到了一直需要的产品。” </p><figure id="attachment_3594312" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594312" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594312" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Judas-Priest.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Judas-Priest.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Judas-Priest-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Judas-Priest-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Judas-Priest-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Judas-Priest-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Judas-Priest-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3594312" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：我们非常关心</figcaption></figure><p>在其他地方，哈尔福德最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priests-rob-halford-on-coming-out-its-never-too-late-to-set-yourself-free-im-fucking-here-im-queer-get-fucking-used-to-it-3788982">回顾了 1998 年他在 MTV 现场表演时如何出柜</a>，他说：“释放自己永远不会太晚，因为我们知道，一旦你出柜，攻击就会消失。我他妈的就在这里，我很奇怪，他妈的习惯吧！” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priests-rob-halford-on-coming-out-its-never-too-late-to-set-yourself-free-im-fucking-here-im-queer-get-fucking-used-to-it-3788982"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> Judas Priest于三月发行了他们的第15张专辑《Invincible Shield》。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priests-rob-halford-isnt-planning-on-retiring-anytime-soon-3792181">《犹大圣徒》的罗布·哈尔福德不打算很快退休：“我不知道我的人生该怎么办”，这</a>句话首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
